ActFisheries Act
Oceans Act
SubjectRegulations Amending Certain Department of Fisheries and Oceans Regulations (Miscellaneous Program)
PrecisRegulations Amending CERTAIN DEPARTMENT OF FISHERIES AND OCEANS REGULATIONS (Miscellaneous Program), by providing more clear and concise Regulations, which will minimize the possibility of misinterpretation of the affected provisions by correcting errors, omissions and inconsistencies. It will also address issues raised by the Standing Joint Committee for the Scrutiny of Regulations.
